<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><title>$ command line ruby cheat sheets</title><link charset="utf-8" href="/style.css" media="screen" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" /></head><body><div class="main"><div class="header"><h1><a href="/">cheat sheets.</a></h1><code class="header">$ command line ruby cheat sheets</code></div></div><div class="content"><pre>Create an auto-mounted EBS Volume on CentOS
---
yum install -y xfsprogs
modprobe xfs
mkfs.xfs /dev/sdh
echo &quot;/dev/sdh /vol xfs noatime 0 0&quot; | sudo tee -a /etc/fstab
mkdir -m 000 /vol
mount -t xfs /vol
